{
  "page": "Shrykos",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><div role=\"note\" class=\"hatnote navigation-not-searchable\" style=\"font-style: italic;padding-left: 1.6em;margin-bottom: 0.5em;\">For the legendary race, see <a href=\"/index.php/Shrykes\" title=\"Shrykes\">Shrykes</a>.</div>\n<table class=\"infobox\" style=\"min-width:22em;max-width:32em;border-collapse:separate;border-spacing:3px\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;font-size:125%;font-weight:bold;font-weight:bold; background: none; line-height: 1.1em;\"><table style=\"width:100%\"><tbody><tr><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:left;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/House_Targaryen\" title=\"House Targaryen\"><img alt=\"House Targaryen.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/1/1e/House_Targaryen.svg/50px-House_Targaryen.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"55\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/1/1e/House_Targaryen.svg/75px-House_Targaryen.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/1/1e/House_Targaryen.svg/100px-House_Targaryen.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:middle;text-align:center;padding:0px 7px 5px 7px\">Shrykos</td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:right;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/House_Targaryen\" title=\"House Targaryen\"><img alt=\"House Targaryen.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/1/1e/House_Targaryen.svg/50px-House_Targaryen.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"55\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/1/1e/House_Targaryen.svg/75px-House_Targaryen.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/1/1e/House_Targaryen.svg/100px-House_Targaryen.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td></tr></tbody></table></th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" class=\"infobox-image\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n<a href=\"/index.php/File:The_unridden_dragons_by_Jota_Saraiva.jpg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"The unridden dragons by Jota Saraiva.jpg\" src=\"/images/thumb/c/c5/The_unridden_dragons_by_Jota_Saraiva.jpg/350px-The_unridden_dragons_by_Jota_Saraiva.jpg\" width=\"350\" height=\"269\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/c/c5/The_unridden_dragons_by_Jota_Saraiva.jpg/525px-The_unridden_dragons_by_Jota_Saraiva.jpg 1.5x, /images/thumb/c/c5/The_unridden_dragons_by_Jota_Saraiva.jpg/700px-The_unridden_dragons_by_Jota_Saraiva.jpg 2x\" /></a><div>Shrykos, Jaehaerys, Morghul, and Jaehaera, by Jota Saraiva</div></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n<hr /></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Owner</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Jaehaerys_Targaryen_(son_of_Aegon_II)\" title=\"Jaehaerys Targaryen (son of Aegon II)\">Jaehaerys Targaryen</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Species</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Dragon\" title=\"Dragon\">Dragon</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Died</th><td>\nIn&#160;<a href=\"/index.php/130_AC\" title=\"130 AC\">130&#160;AC</a>,&#160;the <a href=\"/index.php/Dragonpit\" title=\"Dragonpit\">Dragonpit</a> in <a href=\"/index.php/King%27s_Landing\" title=\"King&#39;s Landing\">King's Landing</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Books</th><td>\n<div class=\"plainlist\"><ul><li><i><a href=\"/index.php/Fire_%26_Blood\" title=\"Fire &amp; Blood\">Fire &amp; Blood</a></i> (mentioned)</li><li><i><a href=\"/index.php/The_Rise_of_the_Dragon\" title=\"The Rise of the Dragon\">The Rise of the Dragon</a></i> (mentioned)</li><li><i><a href=\"/index.php/The_Princess_and_the_Queen\" title=\"The Princess and the Queen\">The Princess and the Queen</a></i> (mentioned)</li><li><i><a href=\"/index.php/The_Rogue_Prince\" title=\"The Rogue Prince\">The Rogue Prince</a></i> (mentioned)</li></ul></div></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p><b>Shrykos</b> was a young she-<a href=\"/index.php/Dragon\" title=\"Dragon\">dragon</a> bound to Prince <a href=\"/index.php/Jaehaerys_Targaryen_(son_of_Aegon_II)\" title=\"Jaehaerys Targaryen (son of Aegon II)\">Jaehaerys Targaryen</a> during the <a href=\"/index.php/Dance_of_the_Dragons\" title=\"Dance of the Dragons\">Dance of the Dragons</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabthe_dying_of_the_dragons_-_rhaenyra_triumphant.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabthe_dying_of_the_dragons_-_rhaenyra_triumphant.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Appearance\">Appearance</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Shrykos&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Appearance\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>Shrykos's coloring is not stated in the books. However, she is depicted as \"copperish\" in an illustration from <i><a href=\"/index.php/The_Rise_of_the_Dragon\" title=\"The Rise of the Dragon\">The Rise of the Dragon</a></i>, as confirmed by the artist Campbell White.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtrotd8.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtrotd8.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup><sup id=\"cite_ref-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"History\">History</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Shrykos&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: History\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"thumb tright\"><div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:202px;\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:Hobbthehewer.png\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/images/thumb/b/bc/Hobbthehewer.png/200px-Hobbthehewer.png\" width=\"200\" height=\"200\" class=\"thumbimage\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/b/bc/Hobbthehewer.png/300px-Hobbthehewer.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/b/bc/Hobbthehewer.png/400px-Hobbthehewer.png 2x\" /></a>  <div class=\"thumbcaption\"><div class=\"magnify\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:Hobbthehewer.png\" class=\"internal\" title=\"Enlarge\"></a></div>Hobb The Hewer by <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://ashleyhunterrice.tumblr.com/\">Ashley Hunter Rice</a></div></div></div>\n<p>Shrykos died in the <a href=\"/index.php/Dragonpit\" title=\"Dragonpit\">Dragonpit</a> when it was <a href=\"/index.php/Storming_of_the_Dragonpit\" title=\"Storming of the Dragonpit\">invaded</a> by a half-crazed angry mob after a one-handed prophet called the <a href=\"/index.php/Shepherd\" title=\"Shepherd\">Shepherd</a> began to rant against all dragons everywhere. Shackled by her heavy chains, Shrykos was slain by a woodsman known as <a href=\"/index.php/Hobb_the_Hewer\" title=\"Hobb the Hewer\">Hobb the Hewer</a> who leapt onto her neck driving his axe into her skull as she roared and twisted, trying to throw him off. With his legs locked around the dragon's neck, Hobb delivered seven blows and each time his axe came down he roared out the name of each of <a href=\"/index.php/The_Seven\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"The Seven\">the Seven</a>. It was the <a href=\"/index.php/Stranger_(the_Seven)\" title=\"Stranger (the Seven)\">Stranger</a>'s blow that slew the dragon, his axe crashed through scale and bones into Shrykos's brain.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabthe_dying_of_the_dragons_-_rhaenyra_overthrown.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_4-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabthe_dying_of_the_dragons_-_rhaenyra_overthrown.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>There is little doubt that Shrykos killed scores of people in the Dragonpit before being slain. Shrykos was never ridden.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabthe_dying_of_the_dragons_-_rhaenyra_overthrown.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_4-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabthe_dying_of_the_dragons_-_rhaenyra_overthrown.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Shrykos&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rfabthe_dying_of_the_dragons_-_rhaenyra_triumphant.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rfabthe_dying_of_the_dragons_-_rhaenyra_triumphant.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/Fire_%26_Blood\" title=\"Fire &amp; Blood\">Fire &amp; Blood</a></i>, The Dying of the Dragons - Rhaenyra Triumphant.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rtrotd8.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rtrotd8.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/The_Rise_of_the_Dragon\" title=\"The Rise of the Dragon\">The Rise of the Dragon</a></i>, The Reign of Aegon II.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-3\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-3\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\">Instagram: <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.instagram.com/p/CkaFwsTuq_9/?igsh=b3RqMGRnb2thZWY%3D\">campbellwhite: \"Storming the Dragonpit\" from George R.R. Martin's \"Rise of the Dragon.\"</a>, November 1, 2022</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rfabthe_dying_of_the_dragons_-_rhaenyra_overthrown.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-4\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rfabthe_dying_of_the_dragons_-_rhaenyra_overthrown.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_4-0\">4.0</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rfabthe_dying_of_the_dragons_-_rhaenyra_overthrown.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_4-1\">4.1</a></sup></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/Fire_%26_Blood\" title=\"Fire &amp; Blood\">Fire &amp; Blood</a></i>, The Dying of the Dragons - Rhaenyra Overthrown.</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n<table cellspacing=\"0\" class=\"navbox\" style=\"border-spacing:0;;\"><tbody><tr><td style=\"padding:2px;\"><table cellspacing=\"0\" class=\"nowraplinks hlist collapsible uncollapsed navbox-inner\" style=\"border-spacing:0;background:transparent;width:100%;color:inherit;;;\"><tbody><tr><th scope=\"col\" style=\";\" class=\"navbox-title\" colspan=\"2\"><div class=\"plainlinks hlist\" style=\"display:block;float:left;font-weight:normal;font-size:88%;padding-top:3px;text-align:left;width:6.8em;\"><ul><li class=\"nv-view\"><a href=\"/index.php/Template:Dragons\" title=\"Template:Dragons\"><span title=\"View this template\" style=\";;background:none transparent;border:none;\">v</span></a></li><li class=\"nv-talk\"><a href=\"/index.php?title=Template_talk:Dragons&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Template talk:Dragons (page does not exist)\"><span title=\"Discuss this template\" style=\";;background:none transparent;border:none;\">d</span></a></li><li class=\"nv-edit\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://awoiaf.westeros.org/index.php?title=Template:Dragons&amp;action=edit\"><span title=\"Edit this template\" style=\";;background:none transparent;border:none;\">e</span></a></li></ul></div><div class=\"\" style=\"font-size:110%;\">\n<a href=\"/index.php/Dragons\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Dragons\">Dragons</a></div></th></tr><tr style=\"height:2px;\"><td></td></tr><tr><td scope=\"row\" class=\"navbox-group\" style=\";;\">Bonded dragons</td><td style=\"text-align:left;border-left-width:2px;border-left-style:solid;width:100%;padding:0px;;;\" class=\"navbox-list navbox-odd\"><div style=\"padding:0em 0.25em\">\n</div><table cellspacing=\"0\" class=\"nowraplinks navbox-subgroup\" style=\"bo